<view class="page wallet-recharge-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">钱包充值</view><view class="form-header-desc">选择充值账户，按当前可用方式完成入账。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">账户选择 <text class="required">*</text></view><view class="grid-two"><view class="{{['check-row', b && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{c}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{a}}</text><view class="wallet-type-copy"><text class="wallet-type-title">保证金账户</text><text class="wallet-type-desc">平台履约保障，账号注销或业务结清后可按规则退还。</text></view></view><view class="{{['check-row', e && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{f}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{d}}</text><view class="wallet-type-copy"><text class="wallet-type-title">信息服务费账户</text><text class="wallet-type-desc">确认接单时扣除信息服务费，每成交一单扣除一次。</text></view></view></view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">支付方式</view><view class="pay-method-list"><view wx:if="{{g}}" class="{{['pay-method-item', j && 'selected']}}" bindtap="{{k}}"><view class="method-left-info"><image class="method-icon" src="{{h}}" mode="aspectFit"/><view class="method-copy"><text class="method-lbl">微信支付</text><text class="method-desc">使用微信收银台完成钱包充值</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{i}}" class="method-selected-badge"><text>已选</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{l}}" class="{{['pay-method-item', 'offline', n && 'selected']}}" bindtap="{{o}}"><view class="method-left-info"><view class="offline-icon">公</view><view class="method-copy"><text class="method-lbl">对公转账</text><text class="method-desc">转账后联系客服，由后台调账入账</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{m}}" class="method-selected-badge offline-badge"><text>已选</text></view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{p}}" class="section"><view class="section-title">充值金额 <text class="required">*</text></view><view class="presets-grid"><view wx:for="{{q}}" wx:for-item="amt" wx:key="b" class="{{['preset-item', 'font-bold', amt.c && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{amt.d}}">{{amt.a}}元 </view></view><view class="field" style="margin-top:30rpx"><text class="label">自定义充值金额 (元)</text><input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="请输入充值金额" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{r}}" bindinput="{{s}}"/></view></view><view wx:if="{{t}}" class="section offline-account-section"><view class="section-title">对公转账信息</view><view class="offline-tip"><text>请通过企业账户转账至以下对公账户，转账后联系客服，由后台核实后为您的{{v}}账户调账入账。</text></view><view class="account-row"><text class="account-label">户名</text><text class="account-value">{{w}}</text><button class="copy-btn" bindtap="{{x}}">复制</button></view><view class="account-row"><text class="account-label">开户行</text><text class="account-value">{{y}}</text><button class="copy-btn" bindtap="{{z}}">复制</button></view><view wx:if="{{A}}" class="account-row"><text class="account-label">开户支行</text><text class="account-value">{{B}}</text><button class="copy-btn" bindtap="{{C}}">复制</button></view><view class="account-row"><text class="account-label">账号</text><text class="account-value mono">{{D}}</text><button class="copy-btn" bindtap="{{E}}">复制</button></view><view class="account-row"><text class="account-label">客服</text><text class="account-value">{{F}}</text><button class="copy-btn" bindtap="{{G}}">复制</button></view><view class="remark-box"><view class="remark-head-row"><text class="remark-label">转账备注信息</text><button class="copy-remark-btn" bindtap="{{H}}">复制全部</button></view><text wx:if="{{I}}" class="remark-text">{{J}}</text><view class="remark-info-list"><view class="remark-info-row"><text class="remark-info-label">企业名称</text><text class="remark-info-value">{{K}}</text><button class="copy-btn compact-copy-btn" bindtap="{{L}}">复制</button></view><view class="remark-info-row"><text class="remark-info-label">注册手机号</text><text class="remark-info-value mono">{{M}}</text><button class="copy-btn compact-copy-btn" bindtap="{{N}}">复制</button></view><view class="remark-info-row"><text class="remark-info-label">充值类型</text><text class="remark-info-value">{{O}}账户</text><button class="copy-btn compact-copy-btn" bindtap="{{P}}">复制</button></view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{Q}}" class="section unavailable-section"><text>当前账户暂未开放充值方式，请联系平台客服。</text></view><view wx:if="{{R}}" class="fixed-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn w-full" loading="{{S}}" bindtap="{{T}}"> 微信支付充值 </button></view></view>